Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不列颠少年鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有两种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,第一是GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能对所有人下达命令 并让其绝对遵从的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,第二是黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为了毁灭他父皇所统治的不列颠帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而属于他的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修使用ZERO这个代号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,展开行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为了替母后报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也为创造让妹妹娜娜莉 能够幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这行动究竟会创造怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 尚无人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:54.90,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仿佛能够改变自己 改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:00.91,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样的瞬间 就在你我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:16.23,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直面难以掩盖的焦躁 正视一动不动的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:23.28,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管迷惑 尽管烦恼 尽管悔恨 决定就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:30.45,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的一句话语 吹走我所有的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:36.79,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我那曾经空荡荡的房间 也迎来了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:44.47,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抬头仰望的天空 万里无云湛蓝无限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:51.00,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}决心去开启 那扇紧锁多年的窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:58.52,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仿佛能够改变自己 改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:04.52,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样的瞬间 现在就去感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:13.82,TITLE,,0,0,0,,抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,河口湖的中心宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,开始重建了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO发布黑色骑士团宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都过去了两周
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还是找不到任何确凿的证据吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,逃离路线不是应该很有限吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在他释放人质后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,从站台上开车进入铁路…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莲…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 这次是梯凳倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,马上收拾!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快到上学的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐 最近您常去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,交到朋友了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说是社会福利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要让给“11区住民”还真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才转到你那里去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 “11区住民”还是减少些比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,报酬就转到您太太的户头上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,柯内莉娅殿下是个武人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对这种事不甚了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开灯! 快开灯!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你、你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真稀罕啊 卡莲居然打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆拜鲁路修为师吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是打瞌睡的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他那样是在睡觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,都不知道他每天晚上到底在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,上课有一半时间在睡觉 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在阿莱曼战线上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,E.U.发动了攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们而言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不能一直被11区牵制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,需将它晋升为永久领区域 从而稳定内政
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为此 虽然剿灭恐怖组织是重要任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但在11区中蔓延的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抑制素也很当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,受此影响 生产力下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,必须在此切断中华联邦的补给路线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是 请多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是 不要再离开租界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,皇姐 关于黑色骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时放任他们一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟欠他们救了你的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 等我回来后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个区域 我会整顿干净后交托于你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 不要想危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗? 尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那个男人 是不列颠皇帝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 你也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那时 ZERO的话中之意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是说还会继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,朱雀 是你的话会怎么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO的行为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,的确很累人啊 双重生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 朱雀 那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 住手啦 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是会长命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明在笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,早…安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没说过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,亚瑟的欢迎会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,趁着还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,得玩的够本呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有准备卡莲的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,作为之前奇怪的话的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你要选哪件?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莲不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是早就戴着了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要去上电视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会很受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么看 电影明星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,话题转得真快…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,少开那种玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后可有够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一天都在接受没完没了的追问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还在澡堂!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这一周连校门都出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 为什么连我们也要被禁止外出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的友情吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不求同年同月同日生 但求同年同月同日死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,出自三国志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是求婚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是说要死也要一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好过份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家又聚在一起 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是该笑的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这也是朱雀君的优点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是有时候想提醒他看看场合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你 那可是犯罪证言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我救了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,自从在宾馆劫持事件中华丽登场后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,世人的目光都聚焦在黑色骑士团身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团正如ZERO所言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是弱者的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,将平民卷入的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮横的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,以及贪污的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,营利主义的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪组织等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这些法律无法制裁的人被单方面裁决了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一夜间成为了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,支持持续增加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至再次得到了Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 这并非是能对外张扬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别闹了 什么黑色骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不能说不列颠的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是“11区住民”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为首领ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了克洛维斯皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在同伴中也有许多人想知道他的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 总觉得若是强迫他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他就会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,或许 我们已经不能失去他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的交流是不是变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,民众为何会协助救了尤菲米娅的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,京都也说要把红莲贰式交给黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,给那种装腔作势的义贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们并非是反抗集团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,证据是他们杀死了草壁中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,中校是自刎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,传闻说他并没有阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,藤堂中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莲小姐 卡莲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西想交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请问要招待去哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,客房吗? 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去我房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说是你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为是男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,日不上学 夜不归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,听说还出入贫民区呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲不在就为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,血缘真是不可违抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因父亲出差而为所欲为的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有些姿色却不长脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是相当复杂的家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,想交给我的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是爷爷拜托我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,学园长?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,中学以来的成绩证明书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是不要在学校给你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已经知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不列颠人与“11区住民”的混血儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那人是我的继母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个打碎花瓶笨手笨脚的女仆 才是我的亲生母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父亲 是史黛菲尔德家的当家吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是被当成佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,又做不了什么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就算怎么被瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也只能傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,明明可以不用住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说白了就是寄生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,赖着以前的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你讨厌你的母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只是觉得厌烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沉重的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,正妻、妾室还有女儿生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,衣食住行也没什么不便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还没到无法忍受的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,即使能容忍一件件小事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,若是叠加到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天会超过负荷的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我喜欢挖掘人家的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不过并不喜欢到处张扬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别在那种地方哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丢脸的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请夸我率直…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 大家都能得救真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏黑色骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要是想裁决犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去当警察不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么不这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得警察办不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,警察这东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,即使现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但成为警察后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,从内部改变不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,即便想去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是会被套上许多枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这只经过种种努力之后才能定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在没有这么做之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的行为无非是自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,自以为是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所说的恶是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,根本评判的标准都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只是单方面的自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你们俩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,先走了 我得先回军队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,下次…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你有时间的话 能否和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙 说他得先回军队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的归宿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抑制素?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,麻药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,特征是能让人觉得回到了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎会很好卖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是对于日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都会觉得怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被不列颠占领前的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是针对日本人的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不能置之不理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等无赖的补给物资一送到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就马上行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,补给也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有不少人想成为同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团真是有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是正义的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,弹药送到后我再联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是说些什么啊“11区住民”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快道歉!道歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,“11区住民”很擅长磕头的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,“11区住民”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对方有5个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那也不能放任不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个被欺负的“11区住民”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你贸然去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然后赢了他们试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那个“11区住民”从明天起 就没法做生意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他自己选择了做不列颠的奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在租界工作 就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的 有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得“11区住民”很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 是想帮他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经腻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,欺负“11区住民”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要不去游戏中心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啧 没有钱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是容易厌倦的一伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不列颠的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 需要加利福尼亚热狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,方便的话来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还有冰淇淋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,11区与日本时代相比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以说好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏成为了不列颠的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,军事与经济也都逐步安定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也能争取市民权
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要去官署办理手续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不也能成为名誉不列颠人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的只有自尊的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我也明白他们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,既后知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修·兰佩尔吉又是怎么想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你的头脑似乎很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,却没有好好利用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,夏莉一直在叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,说鲁鲁从来不肯努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,枉费那出众的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才什么也不做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的“11区住民”肯定也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,向不列颠人低头就能活得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为这样很帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,摆出一副评论家的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对世事冷眼旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对你有少许期待的我 实在是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为你是个正直的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,之前“橘子”事件的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个强夺枢木朱雀事件时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,卿对此没有记忆是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为你会信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上我在新宿事变时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也曾经历过记忆丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当意识恢复时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的苏德兰已经被夺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在失去记忆前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾遇到一名穿学生服的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那名学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我记不起他的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但我认为值得一查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO那家伙在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明明说过要毁灭不列颠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,干的却是协助警察的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 被人感激也不坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,俨然已成为网路英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这样做就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是ZERO的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还真进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道用了什么法术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,名古屋的部份已经完成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很安全啦 在租界里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团 参上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Knightmare果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有一台就压倒性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,日本 日本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我下个月要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是荣誉研究哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还说下次在巴黎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下周的烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,日本的技术是世界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,“抑制素”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了 去留学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,若是不断叠加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天会超过负荷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小心一点 跑太快很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,直人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你得好好看着卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你这女人是何等软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,依赖不列颠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,依赖男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又是靠毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,KnightPolice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是警方的机体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,被跟踪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我调查时 确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明明不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莲 直人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,以Knightmare为对手的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃 你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在你身边 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才一直待在那个家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只为了这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,傻的人是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你能成为不列颠人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你就不会被人欺负了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,打电话、旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都可以随心所欲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是母亲…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,虚假的眼泪 会使人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,虚伪的笑颜 会使自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是药物的后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎无法进行交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,即使回复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也需要相当的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,判决下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,20年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在妈妈出来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要改变世界!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,成为我和妈妈 能正常生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:25.58,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行走山林野路 林中狮虎争吼不绝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:29.45,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天空霞光四射 彼方就是梦中乐土
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:33.32,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}囚禁的孤独中 陷入彷徨的青年问
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.11,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}软弱与愤怒 莫非是我无形的敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.74,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲啊 如今的我 依然难以认清自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:52.41,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兄长们已先行一步 追逐着他们消失的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:59.99,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷茫之夜 明星却向我发出了召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:03.60,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使死去也并非终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:07.39,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使再怎么向往梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:15.24,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真实的你才是我生命的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:19.04,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}狂风凛冽的荒野 却有着蝶舞花开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:22.82,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仿佛四季长春中 嫣嫣绽放的梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:26.59,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正如混浊的纯洁 即使我身染污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:30.50,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请你相信我心中的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:35.99,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲啊 我发誓 不会在人前落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:45.88,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不会让脚边青草上的露珠消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的回忆?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沉浸其中的人真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们确认明天一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.88,0:23:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,又有谁能保证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,既然卡莲想要迈过门槛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:08.48,NEXT,,0,0,0,,红莲舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只能活在今天
